OOC: Jer, are the DED ready to go?

--- Pacifix / Swoop / JetV ---

Swoop nods reluctantly, and enters the ship.

Pacifix smiles his thanks to Ironhide. "Wish us luck, Commander," 
His smiles morphs into a grim determined look, and he starts to 
head towards the ship, after Grimlock, Swoop, and Sludge.


On 21 Jun 2001, at 20:48, robertdahl wrote:

> Grimlock scowled back at Pacifix, hate burning in his red optics.
> Ironhide knew that look, and couldnt have them coming to blows.
> "Grimlock, stand down. Get on the ship, or we will leave you behind."
> he threatened. Grimlock turned his harsh gaze to Ironhide. "Without
> Dinobots, they die on earth." He whispered, and walked towards the
> ship. "Come Swoop, Sludge. We go." he commanded.
